### TASK-31 — Traducciones de la app todo (6 idiomas)

**Archivos:** `apps/todo/i18n/{en,es,it,ca,fr,de}.json`

Extraer todos los textos hardcodeados de `view.tsx`, `widget.tsx` y `admin.tsx`. Estructura de `en.json` (base):

```json
{
  "title": "To-Do",
  "add_placeholder": "New task…",
  "add_button": "Add",
  "pending_label": "{count, plural, one {# pending} other {# pending}}",
  "done_label": "{count, plural, one {# done} other {# done}}",
  "empty": "No tasks yet.",
  "all_done": "All done!",
  "open": "Open →",
  "loading": "Loading…",
  "more_tasks": "+{count} more",
  "admin_title": "To-Do — Admin",
  "admin_subtitle": "{total} total · {pending} pending · {done} done",
  "admin_empty": "No tasks found.",
  "limit_reached": "You've reached the maximum of {max} tasks."
}
```

Traducir a los 5 idiomas restantes (es, it, ca, fr, de). Usar ICU message format para plurales.

